title: NYC Community Health Survey 2006 - NYC Dept. Health and Mental Hygiene (37 Variables)
name: NYC Community Health Survey 2006 - NYC Dept. Health and Mental Hygiene (37 Variables)
description:
PLEASE NOTE: Zeros should be interpreted as null values.  This data includes supplemental information necessary for correct interpretation, available in the attribute detail of this document.

Provides United Hospital Fund boundaries and rates for a number of health topics covering the following health topics: general health status, health care access, cardiovascular health, diabetes, asthma, immunizations, mental health, smoking, second-hand smoke, obesity, commuting patterns, physical activity, cancer screening, HIV, sexual behavior, birth control, drug use, and domestic violence.
